cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.MM 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with learning image embeddings for fashion items and outfits. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper presents an end-to-end model for learning similarity and compatibility between fashion items. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is relevant as the paper discusses the use of the learned representation for various queries. 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is relevant as the paper deals with learning the stylistic relationships between fashion items. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is relevant as the paper deals with image embeddings for fashion items and outfits.
